newritual     "Lesser Ritual of Mastery"                                  #   1
descr "This ritual grants the caster a new first level ritual."
ritpow                 5 # Druidism
level                  1
cost              2   25 # 25 Herbs
newrit                 1 # Caster will learn a new ritual of level 1.
