selectritual "Break the Seventh Seal"
descr "There are Seven Seals that prevent El from punishing the unfaithful.  When the First Seal is broken El will send minions to help his followers and strike at the heretics.  The more seals broken, the more powerful minions will arrive to combat the heretics, but breaking all seven will bring on the Apocalypse which is probably not a good idea.  There is only one set of Seven Seals and multiple El players can cooperate in breaking them."


selectritual "Increase Divine Favor"
descr "The Divine Favor determines how likely it is that help comes from El after at least one of the Seven Seals has been broken.  What this help consists of is determined by the number of seals broken."


selectritual "Bolster Devotion"
descr "This ceremony will increase the power that units receive from being blessed.  The bless effects are per player, so one player doing a Bolster Devotion ceremony will not help other Voice of El players.  The ceremony will cost more and more relics for every time it has been performed."


selectritual "Start Crusade"
descr "This ability calls on the Crusade, which is a formidable army.  The Crusade will go against a player of your choice and continue until that player is annihilated or the Crusade is defeated."


selectritual "Call the Inquisition"
descr "This ability calls on the Inquisition.  The Inquisition will go against all unconverted settlements and make sure they are converted."


selectritual "Summon Champion of Air"
descr "This ritual summons a supernatural commander from the Elemental Plane of Air."


selectritual "Summon Mist Warriors"
descr "This ritual summons a group of para-elemental Mist Warriors and binds them into servitude. Mist Warriors are composed of the elemental aspects of air and water."


